12 feb 98 Version 1.9
Change:New way to print files that are more than just (!) twice
       on the drive. Now, if you got let's say 8 copies of the
       same file, they'll be listed "8 in a row" and no more
       2 per 2.
       This feature was suggested a long time ago by Mikko
       Venäläinen (thanks dude :)
