       by me, so maybe you'll have something weird :P )
  Add: Up-to-date Deutsch catalog file (same as above)
  Add: Some changes in the guide.

08 feb 98 Version 1.8

  Add: Up-to-date Swenska catalog file.
  Add: A few changes in the guides.

04 feb 98 Version 1.8
  Add: Thanks to the help of Jörg Strohmayer, I was able to get rid
